  Added dev-util/pkgconfig to DEPEND.

*msmtp-1.2.2 (01 Sep 2004)

  01 Sep 2004; Andrej Kacian <ticho@gentoo.org> +msmtp-1.2.2.ebuild:
  Version bump. Closes #60609, reported by Daniel Webert
  <rockoo@rockoo.homelinux.org>. Also specified minimal version number for
  dev-libs/openssl dependency to 0.9.6 (according to upstream doc) for
  msmtp-1.2.2 and -1.2.1.

  10 Aug 2004; Tom Martin <slarti@gentoo.org> msmtp-1.2.1.ebuild:
  Add virtual/libc DEPEND.

